//dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Choose edition Search singapore asia world opinion life business sport Visual Podcasts SPH Rewards\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"Paid press releases\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"Advertise\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 142}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sports news\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 220}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP PublishedJan 23, 2024, 02:09 PM UpdatedNov 08, 2024, 01:43 PM PARIS-From the windows of Les Bons Vivants cafe, a short walk from the athletes' villagefor the Paris Olympics,the changes under way in the once run-down neighbourhood are instantly visible.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999983624548, \"rank\": 1.6238857345737253e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"PM\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"UpdatedNov\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"the windows\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"Les Bons Vivants cafe\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"a short walk\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"the once run-down neighbourhood\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next door, the makeover of the 130-metre Tour Pleyel skyscraper is nearly complete, turning the 1970s eyesore into a modern landmark that will host a four-star hotel and a pool with panoramic views.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the makeover\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the 130-metre Tour Pleyel skyscraper\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1970s eyesore\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"a modern landmark\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-star hotel\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"panoramic views\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its private owner started the \\u20ac500 million (S$728.2 million) renovation in anticipation of an Olympics dividend for the Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine area, which has been a focus of public investment for the July 26-Aug 11 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its private owner\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"S$728.2 million) renovation\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"anticipation\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics dividend\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine area\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"public investment\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"-Aug\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around the corner from the cafe, a newly completed apartment block with a modern facade of concrete and wood stands opposite relics of the past - scruffy two-storey brick buildings hosting garages and kebab shops.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"score\": 0.7992708389058141, \"rank\": 0.2511403535866476, \"text\": \"kebab\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the cafe\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a newly completed apartment block\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"a modern facade\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"concrete\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"wood\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"opposite relics\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"the past - scruffy two-storey brick buildings\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"garages\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A brand-new station - Saint-Denis Pleyel - is also emerging from a mass of cranes and scaffolding, set to one day be a hub for four metro lines and 250,000 daily travellers.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A brand-new station - Saint-Denis Pleyel\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"a mass\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"cranes\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"scaffolding\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a hub\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"four metro lines\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"250,000 daily travellers\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's taking time but after the Games, it's going to be good,\\\" said Ethan, a 28-year-old waiter at Les Bons Vivants.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"Ethan\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"a 28-year-old waiter\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"Les Bons Vivants\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As soon as they are finished, all the infrastructure will be for the town.\\\"\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the infrastructure\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"the town\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The emerging modernity outside contrasts with life inside the bar.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The emerging modernity\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With its formica tables, old wooden bar and staff in traditional black waistcoats and white aprons, time appears to have stood still.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its formica tables\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"old wooden bar\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional black waistcoats\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"white aprons\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The meeting of the new and old in Saint-Ouen is causing some tensions and fears, Ethan admits.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6554647092368376e-57, \"text\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The meeting\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"some tensions\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"Ethan\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"House prices have gone crazy and it's going to change the population, it's undeniable,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House\", \"score\": 0.9999999999713509, \"rank\": 2.8803839807571087e-11, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint-Ouen lies just to the north of Paris, separated from the capital by the ring road that divides the generally wealthy and mostly white centre of the city from its more deprived, immigrant-heavy suburbs.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6554647092368376e-57, \"text\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6950913515552135e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the north\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring road\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"the generally wealthy and mostly white centre\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"its more deprived, immigrant-heavy suburbs\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known for its 150-year-old flea market and for once hosting the famed Pleyel piano factory, Saint-Ouen is also associated with the modern scourges of Paris' suburbs - run-down tower blocks and drug-dealing.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ignaz_Pleyel\", \"score\": 0.9996149553543402, \"rank\": 0.00026789895421940534, \"text\": \"Pleyel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ignaz_Pleyel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ignaz_Pleyel\"}, {\"begin\": 2295, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6554647092368376e-57, \"text\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6950913515552135e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its 150-year-old flea market\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern scourges\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"drug-dealing\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision to place the athletes' village there and extend two metro lines into the area - another three are planned in the future - was part of the pitch for the Paris Games, which French authorities won in 2017.\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8829254911149557, \"rank\": 0.13205167256578978, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"two metro lines\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as the 2012 London Olympics helped regenerate the eastern Stratford area of the British capital, Paris organisers believe their Games will help develop Saint-Ouen and the surrounding areas of the notorious Seine-Saint-Denis district.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2713, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999527470268343, \"rank\": 4.5935808175695237e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6950913515552135e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2839, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2012 London Olympics\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"the eastern Stratford area\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"their Games\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"the surrounding areas\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Buildings at the construction site of the 2024 Olympic Villlage in Saint-Denis, north of Paris on Jan 15.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 0.9945217529884353, \"rank\": 0.005507463374085044, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6950913515552135e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Buildings\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction site\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Villlage\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"north\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"Jan\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP \\\"I guess we are part of the gentrification process,\\\" admits local resident Maite Gallen, 37, a psychologist who moved to Saint-Ouen from Paris with her husband \\\"to have a bit more space\\\".\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3108, \"end\": 3118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6554647092368376e-57, \"text\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Ouen-sur-Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6950913515552135e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"the gentrification process\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"local resident Maite Gallen\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"a psychologist\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit more space\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In terms of the impact of the Games, I am sceptical,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess it's a good thing overall, but they came here and did a big presentation about the future 'international attractiveness' of Saint-Ouen which made me laugh.\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good thing\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3268}, {\"ngram\": \"a big presentation\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"the future 'international attractiveness\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not quite there yet.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not even find a supermarket nearby.\\\"\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a supermarket\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She hopes, though, the new village that will house competitors and officials for the Games will bring positive changes.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new village\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"offici